    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just bots or scraping. that's the thing. the posts are so specific. it's like it knows my inside jokes and even the way I get annoyed at certain things. if it's not hijacking me, how does it know my personality so well? it feels like my digital self has become a separate entity that's just... running on autopilot. doesn't that sound like something a sophisticated AI could do?",
