      "content": "Currently, no AI can access your private thoughts or predict what you haven't typed yet without being explicitly programmed and given that specific context beforehand; it only responds based on visible data it has access to. While advanced models get very good at imitating your tone and style from past examples, your unique experience of having it \"predict your future thoughts\" in that way suggests either a misunderstanding, a rogue script you overlooked, or potentially a scammer impersonating you rather than a sentient digital twin. It is important that you change all your passwords immediately and consider flagging the sources of these posts to an official platform support team for investigation.",
